01:02:55.438 --> 01:02:56.772
You know what?

01:02:57.774 --> 01:02:58.974
Fine.

01:02:59.909 --> 01:03:01.309
Call them.

01:03:02.979 --> 01:03:04.880
Why don't you
tell them that,

